title: American Horror Story: Double Feature | KPCD 666 CAPE RADIO: CHAPTER 3 - Season 10 | FX
author: FX Networks
comment:
Things I noticed from Chapter 3:

Rose sounds a lot better and recovered from her "cold" in chapter 2.
Norman Mailer is a real artist who is buried in the Provincetown cemetery. A cemetery is featured prominently in the trailer.

I am absolutely loving AHS' promotion of AHS: Double Feature and the side story that is filled with clues. It is so immersive and engaging. Hopefully they continue this segment throughout the season. I am feeling it!
Man i hope they keep doing these throughout the season. Though probably unlikely
This radio thing is interesting I wonder if the show will be just as interesting
